      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"6. FERGIE'S GIRL was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 17.47. Jumping from the pinch draw but has the early speed to avoid trouble. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. 8. THAT'S THAT was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by 4 lengths (17.23) at this track. Leading player again. 1. SPACE CONSPIRACY hit the frame last time at this track but just a few starts ago ran blistering time when scoring over 305m at this track in 17.42. Top win three back and rates a key player again from the ace box. 4. CLAWS IN SPARKY was in the money last start and likely to feature again. Odds will be appealing.\",\"runners\":[6,8,1,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
